name: Victoria
description:
I work in pathology and have a wide range of passions including painting/drawing, music and good food. Love learning new things and experiencing new places. Need to know more, feel free to ask 🙂
I love a good uncontrollable belly laugh, and whilst I can be serious, I also enjoy being ridiculous. If you were to meet me you would probably think I am extroverted, but I am actually more of an introvert. I love furry animals, yeah I know that’s not fair to the reptiles but that’s just how I feel. There are times when I will be extremely healthy for months, but then I might go through a period of a month where I’m not – I’m not overly regimented or consistent in life. Also, I’m not on this site for a bit of fun. I’m ready to meet someone more seriously but please don’t take that as desperation!!
